      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that still has plenty of life left? This car is a solid, honest performer in fair condition, showing some expected character and wear from its years on the road but still running strong! It's the perfect choice for someone who values reliable transportation and a great driving experience over a showroom finish. Come see why this well-loved vehicle is ready for its next chapter with you!",
