    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy. The engine currently has a persistent knock and noticeable oil leaks, and the transmission is hesitant when shifting into higher gears. The exterior shows its age with significant rust on the wheel arches and several deep scratches, while the interior has multiple tears in the fabric and a non-functional climate control system. This would be an ideal project car for someone with mechanical expertise or a source for specific parts.",
