      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is offered in showroom-quality condition, having been maintained to the highest possible standards. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, reflects a life of meticulous care. This is not merely a pre-owned vehicle; it is a benchmark for the model, offering the discerning driver an experience indistinguishable from new. A rare opportunity to acquire a masterpiece of engineering in a state of absolute preservation.",
      "price": 48900.0,
